                      "value": "作者: Roshan Sharma, Suyoun Kim, Daniel Lazar, Trang Le, Akshat Shrivastava, Kwanghoon Ahn, Piyush Kansal, Leda Sari, Ozlem Kalinli, Michael Seltzer"
                    }
